{
  "stem": "4189.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this particular Sonderkommando that was there at that time-- that was already in 1944, that happened-- they knew that their time was coming, that they were going to kill them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they wanted to make an uprising.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They wanted to blow up this crematoria.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were all together three of them-- three or four of those crematorias.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think there was three or four.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't even remember anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But anyway, they wanted to blow that up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they wanted to make an uprising.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they contacted the Polish resistance that was on the outside-- civilian Polish resistance, for help, for arms.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they could get-- couldn't get any help from them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, they knew, that in that factory-- where I worked, and where the women were working with that dynamite-- they knew that there was dynamite there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they contacted these women and they asked them to smuggle out dynamite, to bring it out into the camp, so that they could use that dynamite.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, the only way-- they couldn't take it in packages and take it out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would have caught them right away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what they did, they did it in the seam of their clothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every day, they put a little bit of this dynamite, and hid it inside the clothing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they brought it out that way, until one day, they had enough dynamite that they felt they had enough to blow up this crematoria.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they actually did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They blew up the crematoria and the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they killed several of the guards, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But all these 400 guys that worked in that kommando, they were all killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they did manage to blow up the crematoria and the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
